name: Coin collector (Sinlesss)
description:
You are bored?

You dont know how to spend your time?

Spend your time in Coin collector !

Start small with two blocks and collect more coins to unlock new blocks.Use a keyboard or a controler to move the player in the left or right direction.Click on the bottom of the screen to open the shop and buy new blocks.

For every time a block collide with something you earn coins!

Are you able get into the leaderboard ?

Thanks for playing  :)
